  15 Dec 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> +noto-sans-cjk-jp-1.004.ebuild,
  -noto-sans-cjk-jp-9999.ebuild:
  Add version 1.004, delete version 9999

   This package is picking files from the repository, because it's too large.
  Therefore it is better to change strict versioning for avoiding digests
  fails.

  25 Nov 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> noto-sans-cjk-jp-9999.ebuild:
